data.description:
WOW! Nice home in large corner lot. 3 BR/ 2 BA. Large living room,Newer master bath. Plus garage conv.to family room with custom solid wood built-ins. Could be 4th bedroom (permit Unknow) buyer to verify all information. property begin sold in its current AS IS physical condition. hardwood flooring throughout move in condition . Lovely front and large backyard w/many fruit trees, close, store, shopping and Bart. Easy access to Fwy 580, 238 & 880. Hurry! Wont Last Long.
LARGE CORNER LOT!)
